(42, 23, 40, 66, 15, 4, 4, 'Dost not thou fear God', 'Fear of God and Worship', 'This connection highlights the theme of fearing God present in both passages. In Luke, the rebuke emphasizes the need for reverence in the face of condemnation, while Revelation calls all nations to fear and glorify God for His holiness and judgments.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
