(42, 23, 43, 54, 1, 15, 16, NULL, 'Salvation and Eternal Life', 'Both passages emphasize the promise of salvation and eternal life through Jesus. In Luke, Jesus assures the thief of being in paradise, while in 1 Timothy, Paul speaks of Jesus coming to save sinners, highlighting the transformative power of faith.', 'theme', 0.6639999999999999, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
