(42, 23, 43, 43, 14, 3, 3, 'with me in paradise', 'Promise of Eternal Presence', 'This connection highlights the promise of being with Jesus. Both passages emphasize the idea of being together with Him in a prepared place.', 'theme', 0.573, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
